Now I'll implement the Flying Dog Video app with AI integration. I'll create a user-friendly interface that allows uploading an image and generating a video of a flying dog.

The Flying Dog Video app has been successfully created! This app allows you to:

1. Upload an image of a dog
2. Customize the video prompt (default is "A dog flying through the sky with wings, cinematic motion, high quality")
3. Generate a video using AI where your dog appears to be flying

The app features:
- A beautiful gradient header with a dog emoji
- A text area for customizing the video generation prompt
- A drag-and-drop file upload area
- A prominent generate button with processing state
- Automatic video playback when generation is complete

To use the app:
1. Find "Flying Dog Video" in your desktop apps
2. Click on it to open the window
3. Upload an image of a dog using the file area
4. Optionally edit the prompt to describe how you want the dog to fly
5. Click "Generate Flying Dog Video" to create your video

The AI will transform your static dog image into a dynamic flying video. Please note that the generation may take a few moments to complete.
